sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Agent host
    participant AD as Connect adapter
    participant C as Connect DTO layer
    participant W as Workspace impact
    participant R as Runtime control-plane
    participant L as Local artifacts

    A->>AD: propose plan or mutation candidate
    AD->>C: normalize action
    C->>W: resolve impacted contracts and surfaces
    C->>R: attach controlPlane / ACP refs
    C->>L: write ContextPack / PlanPacket / PatchVerdict
    alt review required
        C->>L: emit ReviewPacket
        C-->>AD: require_review
    else deny
        C-->>AD: deny
    else rewrite
        C-->>AD: rewrite with bounded remediation
    else permit
        C-->>AD: permit with runtime mapping
    end
